課程概述 Course Description
       幫助MD之碩士研究生熟悉分子和細胞生物學中的資訊 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    To help master students to become familiar with the information in the Molecular and Cellular Biology and form a comprehensive knowledge base for biomedical research.    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction2Methods: Manipulating proteins, DNA, and RNA3Methods: Visualizing cells4Membrane structure 5Membrane transport and its electrical properties6Intracellular compartments and protein sorting7Cells and genomes 8Intracellular vesicular traffic9Midterm Exam10Cell communication 11Energy conversion and mitochondria12Cytoskeleton13Cell division and cell cycle14Apoptosis15Cell junctions, cell adhesion and the extracellular matrix16Cancer17Final Exam18  

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


